::Kluster::

Kluster looks around for a new target, seeing a Decepticon fighting 
with a Maximal. Not wanting to accidently hit Khonokolor with a 
missile, he takes out a rifle, aiming it carefully and firing two 
blasts at Razorclaw's head.
